## 10. Documentation Standards in Pull Requests
All PRs involving documentation will contain the following:
- Use clear and concise language
- Define acronyms on first use
- Maintain consistent terminology
- Follow project style guidelines
- Ensure content is accessible and understandable

---

## 11. Compliance and Secuirty Considerations
- No sensitive or controlled informaiton will be included in PRs
- All changes shall comply with applicable DHS and project policies
- Access to repositories shall follow approved security protocols

